{
  "stem": "13141.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, we landed-- just before we landed, the loudspeaker system on the ship announced that we were landing in England-- in Liverpool, England.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's actually when we knew where we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there, again, we were trained.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were going to the firing range, as I was in the artillery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was in the Fire Direction Center, where you would-- Headquarters Battery-- where you calculated the elevation of the-- of the-- pieces, we called them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The cannons, actually, but we called them pieces-- the artillery, how they had to be adjusted, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, the angle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we had to adjust for the-- the meteorological messages, you know, according to the direction of the wind, and the humidity, and the-- because all that influenced the direction of the flight, and you had to adjust for all that.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was, what they called at the time, a computer, with a slide rule, you know, in the Fire Direction Center.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I got there, actually, in England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before, I was a machine gun [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in England, again, we had maneuvers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then about one month before the landing-- we didn't know where the landing was, but they showed us, in miniature, where we were going to land.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were many buildings there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were the roads there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were the hedge rows-- the famous hedge rows in France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a pretty good idea, where we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We only knew that it was going to be in France, but not where.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we started the landing maneuvers, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went on lakes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the very last, maybe two weeks, before we shipped across, our outfit went to Swansea.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
